"WARRIORS" ,2005,11
The Gangwar comes to its shattering conclusion-this is one ending you don't want to miss! Who lives? Who dies? Who will betray Spider-Man?! And what happens when the spark of romance is rekindled between Spidey and the Black Cat? Let the fur fly! Part 7 (of 7).
32 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$2.50
column8: | penciller (cover):Mark Bagley | writer:Brian Michael Bendis | letterer:Chris Eliopoulos | inker:Scott Hanna | colorist:J. D. Smith
